reviews.text: Accidentally passed by this mysterious underground  restaurant at lunch! Price is reasonable cheap for TST area. Cheapest set lunch for set lunch of cabbage soup BBQ sliced beef with rice for main dish 2 snacks of kimchi and spinach plus a soft drink of your choice. The set is only HK$42. Hope to try other dishes if on my way again.
Good and very fresh food, especially the sea food. The service is also not bad.

Great place for KBBQ! Well ventilated & comfortable.
Worth to get the upgrade to the premium meats & seafood.
Food very nice, reasonable price, good service. Highly recommend
Good food with good service!
